---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Fody Labs" description="Learn about Fody Labs — 25+ years building desktop, web, and mobile software.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="section-label">About Us</p>
      <h1 class="page-title">Engineering Runs Deep</h1>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Since the late 1990s we&rsquo;ve been shipping production software &mdash;
        from COM/ActiveX components to modern cross-platform mobile apps.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="about-heading">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          Fody Labs started as a one-person consultancy and grew into a focused
          engineering studio. Over 25&plus; years we&rsquo;ve worked with startups,
          enterprises, and everything in between &mdash; always hands-on,
          always code-first.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Today we specialize in .NET MAUI mobile development, building apps
          that feel native on every platform while sharing a single codebase.
          We combine deep platform knowledge with modern AI tooling to ship
          faster without cutting corners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="about-heading">How We Work</h2>
        <div class="values">
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Code-First</h3>
            <p>We write code, review code, and ship code. No committees, no slide decks.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Lean &amp; Direct</h3>
            <p>Small team, fast decisions. You talk directly to the engineer building your product.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>Ship Early</h3>
            <p>Working software over documentation. We iterate in short cycles with real builds.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value">
            <h3>AI-Augmented</h3>
            <p>We use AI tools daily to accelerate development &mdash; not replace engineering judgment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <h2 class="section-title">Timeline</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-year">1999</span>
        <p>Started building desktop applications with Delphi and C++</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-year">2005</span>
        <p>Transitioned to .NET ecosystem &mdash; WinForms, WPF, ASP.NET</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-year">2015</span>
        <p>First mobile projects with Xamarin</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-year">2022</span>
        <p>Adopted .NET MAUI for cross-platform mobile development</p>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-year">2024</span>
        <p>Integrated AI tooling into daily engineering workflow</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding-top: 8rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 0%, var(--color-accent-glow) 0%, transparent 50%),
      var(--color-bg);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .about-heading {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .values {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .value {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .value h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .value p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    min-width: 3rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
